    Style package information as knitr kable.

    style_package_information_as_kable.Rd

    Provide a kable formatted output for the package information.

    style_package_information_as_kable(packages)

    Arguments

    packages

    The packages tibble from session_info

    Value

    Kable-formatted package information.

    Examples

    style_package_information_as_kable(get_package_information())
